Class SimpleEmitter

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Emitter
    Deprecated. 
    Use the BatchEmitter, or create your own Emitter using the provided interface.

    @Deprecated
public class SimpleEmitter
extends AbstractEmitter
    An emitter which sends events one-by-one as soon as they are received, via GET requests. The events are sent asynchronously.
